<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Weasel" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Weasel,</orth> the animal Mustela vulgaris: <bibl n="shak. luc 307" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 307</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.396" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 396</bibl>. Sucking eggs: <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.5.13" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 5, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 1.2.170" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 I, 2, 170</bibl>. Full of spleen and quarrelsome: <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.3.81" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 3, 81</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.4.162" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 4, 162</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>